INSERT INTO `movies` VALUES (1,'Jaoquin Phoenix, Lady Gaga','Todd Phillips','Joker: Folie à Deux','Bradley Cooper','R','4.5','Joker: Folie à Deux is an upcoming American musical psychological thriller film slated to be a sequel to the 2019 film Joker.','https://static0.cbrimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joker-folie-a-deux-2024.jpg','https://www.youtube.com/embed/03ymBj144ng?si=776k2iZ-34FMkE3e','Now Showing','Crime, Drama','12','8','10'),(2,'Kingsley Ben-Adir, Lashana Lynch, Michael Gandolfini','Reinaldo Marcus Green','Bob Marley: One Love','Ziggy Marley','PG-13','3.9','Bob Marley: One Love is a 2024 biographical music-drama film directed by Reinaldo Marcus Green. The film covers three years of Bob Marley\'s life, from 1976 to 1978, and includes archive footage. Kingsley Ben-Adir portrays Marley, and Lashana Lynch plays his wife, Rita','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71HnzSXm09L.jpg','https://www.youtube.com/embed/ajw425Kuvtw?si=9FG_SeN3pix5xv2_','Now Showing','Musical, Drama','12','8','10'),(3,'Lea Seydoux, George MacKay','Bertrand Bonello','La Bête','Xavier Dolan','PG-13','4.9','In the near future where emotions have become a threat, Gabrielle finally decides to purify her DNA in a machine that will immerse her in her previous lives and rid her of any strong feelings. She then meets Louis and feels a powerful connection, as if she has known him forever.','https://filmartgallery.com/cdn/shop/products/the-beast-la-bete-vintage-movie-poster-original-german-a1-23x33-8063.jpg?v=1663222255','https://www.youtube.com/embed/SYDxOkp19kQ?si=Gop-0I1YLrVjKIyO','Coming Soon','Thriller, Romance','12','8','11'),(4,'Adele Exarchopoulous, Francois Civil','Gilles Lellouche','L\'Amour Ouf','Alain Attal','PG-13','2.2','Beating Hearts is a 2024 French movie directed by Gilles Lellouche. It is about a rebellious teenager named Clotaire and his classmate Jackie whose bond is tested when Clotaire gets caught up in gang violence and ends up in prison on trumped-up murder charges.','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzA2YzRmNzUtZTcxMy00ZDkzLWJhNDItZDlmY2MzYTBkMDBiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTc3NDUyNTg3._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_.jpg','https://www.youtube.com/embed/93JHxbzzzjU?si=B-5TVmoY9PDlOUzj','Coming Soon','Comedy, Romance','11','7','9'),(5,'Florence Pugh, Harry Styles','Olivia Wilde','Don’t Worry Darling','Katie Silberman','R','3.6','Don’t Worry Darling is a psychological thriller set in an experimental utopian community in the 1950s. The film follows a young housewife as she uncovers disturbing truths about her husband’s involvement in the secretive community’s unsettling and dangerous projects.','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71yno6PByYL._AC_UF894,1000_QL80_.jpg','https://www.youtube.com/embed/sSmBIIGZoGI?si=NZYQdqk8uPBXmOul','Now Showing','Thriller, Drama','12','8','11'),(6,'Jason Schwartzman, Scarlett Johansson','Wes Anderson','Asteroid City','Steven Rales','PG-13','4.2','Asteroid City is a 2024 American comedy-drama directed by Wes Anderson. Set in a fictional desert town during a junior stargazer/parent convention, the film intertwines the lives of its eccentric characters as they navigate a blend of romantic, cosmic, and existential crises against a backdrop of mid-century Americana.','https://www.movieposters.com/cdn/shop/files/asteroid_city_ver2_510x.jpg?v=1685457857','https://www.youtube.com/embed/7CdPhrCRc3o?si=FqxrweS86gOcYYAf','Now Showing','Comedy, Drama','12','8','10');
